//How to
How to use the app: Press anywhere on the camera screen to start the search. The app will analyze the image and search the database using the word(s) with the highest size. Please place the text you are about to scan as close to the camera as possible for the best result. The app will store the last 10 items You found with Your searches. Click on any of these to load and view them again The results will be displayed in a list with information obtained from Läkemedelsverket. Click on the list titles to display different information. The active substances are clickable and marked so with an icon. Click on one to search Google for the substance
